@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam responseMessageAlign center

title 企业RAG 用户问答数据流 - ReAct Agent 循环

actor "浏览器\n(Vue 3)" as Browser
participant "M1: Spring Boot\n(ChatHandler)" as M1
participant "M2: DeepSeek API" as M2
participant "M6: Redis" as M6
participant "M4: Elasticsearch" as M4
participant "M5: MySQL" as M5

Browser -> M1: WebSocket连接(携带JWT)
activate M1
M1 -> M6: 查Token有效性
M6 --> M1: Token有效
M1 -> M2: ReAct请求(用户问题+工具定义+历史)
M2 --> M1: 流式推送tool_calls chunk
M1 -> M4: KNN+BM25混合检索
M4 --> M1: 返回SearchResult topK
M1 -> Browser: 流式推送token chunk
Browser -> Browser: 停止生成信号

note right of M1
  <b>ReAct循环</b>
  - 最多4轮
  - 最多8次工具调用
  - 超时120秒
  - 可随时取消
end note

note right of Browser
  <b>流式输出</b>
  - 逐token推送
  - 50-200ms间隔
  - 打字机效果
end note

@enduml
